videos.headline: Oregon State jumps out to early lead
videos.description: Ryan Nall powers through for 4 yd TD run to give Beavers 10-0 lead

videos.headline: Cal gets tricky with fake punt
videos.description: Cal punter Dylan Klumph throws a 4th down pass to Evan Weaver who rushes 11 yards for a 1st down against Oregon State.

videos.headline: Beavers add to lead
videos.description: Darell Garretson runs for 25 yd TD to take 17-3 lead

videos.headline: Pick six for Cal!
videos.description: Raymond Davison intercepts Darell Garretson pass and returns for 39 yd TD

videos.headline: Oregon State makes a statement with wild 80-yard TD run
videos.description: Ryan Nall rushes 80 yards for a second-half touchdown to give the Beavers a 24-10 lead over Cal.

videos.description: Davis Webb runs for 1 yd TD to cut Oregon State lead to 27-17
